title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Native C-17 Globemaster
description:
Earlier this week we already looked at the C-17 Globemaster. However in this video we are going to look at the native version of the C-17 Globemaster which is still in the alpha phase of the development cycle. Although it is in the early development phase I had a brief look at the aircraft and spotted some nice features in it.

If you want to try the aircraft yourself please download it from the site below:
https://flightsim.to/file/12408/msfs-native-c-17-globemaster
